once upon a time in a forest there lived a monkey who recided in a berry tree which was under banks of river
in the same forest there lived the crocodile and his wife.One day the crocodile came to the banks of the river
and rested under the tree the kind hearted monkey offered him fruits the crocodile came back next day for more
fruits. As days past crocodile and monkey became best friends next day crocodile went back home and told about 
monkey to his wife